this lake looks, I guess...

43:56.968 --> 44:00.586
...compared to this fucked-up
reality we live in. I don't know.

44:01.056 --> 44:04.423
Oh. Okay. Hey, just take a breath.

44:05.352 --> 44:07.263
Just breathe. Oh, baby.

44:11.525 --> 44:13.607
