46:00.425 --> 46:01.926
Bill is inside the house.

46:02.093 --> 46:04.584
How is channeling nature's memory
gonna help?

46:04.763 --> 46:06.754
History teaches us great lessons.

46:06.932 --> 46:10.925
We need to look to it, find some answers.

46:11.770 --> 46:13.761
Give me your hands.

46:24.282 --> 46:26.068
[CAROLINE WAILING]

46:26.242 --> 46:28.324
