46:28.536 --> 46:29.912
[GROANING]

46:32.374 --> 46:33.580
[BABY WAILING]

46:33.750 --> 46:35.866
NURSE:
Mr. Compton, please come in.

46:36.711 --> 46:38.121
[BABY CRYING]

46:38.296 --> 46:40.708
NURSE:
Congratulations, Mr. Compton.

46:40.882 --> 46:42.668
Hi, sweetheart.

46:42.884 --> 46:44.840
Hi, sweetie. She's perfect.

46:45.428 --> 46:46.508
[BABY CRYING]

46:46.680 --> 46:48.090
Wow.

46:48.390 --> 46:50.255
"WOW," What?

46:51.267 --> 46:53.758
Didn't you think that was amazing?

46:53.937 --> 46:56.428
