46:57.482 --> 47:00.098
Bill's wife gave birth.

47:00.652 --> 47:01.983
SO what?

47:02.153 --> 47:03.814
"SO what?"

47:04.614 --> 47:06.991
Was I not clear before?

47:08.410 --> 47:11.652
Because I thought I made myself
perfectly clear...

47:11.830 --> 47:14.196
...when I said I was looking for a miracle.

47:14.374 --> 47:17.662
-That was a miracle.
-BabieS are born all the time.

47:17.836 --> 47:20.828
That doesn't make it less miraculous.

47:21.006 --> 47:23.748
There's magic in the ordinary, Sook.

47:23.925 --> 47:26.541
There's magic in the things we can see.

47:26.720 --> 47:30.508
Birth is a miracle. Love is a miracle.

47:30.682 --> 47:33.344
Death is a miracle.

47:34.060 --> 47:36.301
Forgiveness is a miracle.

47:36.771 --> 47:41.811
Especially if you can learn
to forgive yourself.

47:46.740 --> 47:50.983
Did you bring me here to Bill's house...

47:52.454 --> 47:54.194
...just to trick me?

47:54.372 --> 47:56.363
NO, sweet orphan.

47:56.541 --> 48:02.081
I brought you here
because I wanted to give you some advice.

48:02.547 --> 48:07.257
There are some things
that can be fixed with magic.

48:07.844 --> 48:12.884
But your vampire friend is not one of them.

48:13.058 --> 48:14.423
I'm sorry.

48:22.233 --> 48:25.020
